Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}快點快點啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}妳想要幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}妳想...妳想要作什麼啊知美？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}到底是怎樣毛利先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}毛利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}我咧...
